<p>Follow these steps to purchase QuantConnect Credit (QCC):</p>

<ol>
    <li>Open the <a href="/docs/v2/our-platform/organizations/billing#03-View-Billing-Information">Billing</a> page.</li>
    <li>Scroll down to the <span class="page-section-name">Organization Credit (QCC)</span> section and then click <span class="button-name">Purchase Credit</span>.</li>
    <li>Select a credit pack and then click <span class="button-name">Continue</span>.</li>
    <li>If your preferred organization has a credit card and you want to charge that card, click <span class="button-name">Purchase</span>.</li>
    <li>If your preferred organization doesn't have a credit card, enter the credit card details and then click <span class="button-name">Purchase</span>.</li>
        <p>Only the preferred organization can be charged when purchasing QCC. If you want to charge a different organization you are a member of, <a href="/docs/v2/our-platform/organizations/administration#10-Set-a-Preferred-Organization">set it as your preferred organization</a>.</p>
</ol>